    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 local-id=\"653ac13b-4485-40f3-b370-7f2a4e94d3da\" id=\"RenderManforKatanaReleaseNotes-WelcometoRenderManforKatana!\"><style>[data-colorid=b7brxvuad2]{color:#808284} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=b7brxvuad2]{color:#7b7d7f}</style>Welcome to RenderMan for Katana!</h3><p local-id=\"6ae3c49e-c280-401b-b5c9-a5bf18bac16d\">RenderMan for Katana (RfK) capitalizes on the changes made for newer versions of Katana and continues full support of the latest RenderMan.&nbsp; See the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542238759/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RenderMan Release Notes</a> for more details.</p><p local-id=\"f7895944-81bf-43ab-9284-5a7599cfdf95\">This current release offers support for:</p><ul local-id=\"5e691401-8a3b-4579-bf0d-d39051112cde\"><li local-id=\"9ca9e924-2bd7-4bc9-8f58-77a7550dabbd\"><p local-id=\"9b68bd0b-0075-40b1-8af7-2ea35c8cef6c\">Katana 8.0</p></li><li local-id=\"9eac1a07-9682-4743-823e-01c828fec63a\"><p local-id=\"fbea8deb-27ce-4f9b-85bc-a2e57e262ac5\">Katana 7.5</p></li><li local-id=\"0fb6dc4e-ea44-4c8a-a288-61fb54931a52\"><p local-id=\"457e6cc6-6023-4095-bc12-aba5b3383951\">Katana 7.0</p></li></ul><h4 local-id=\"14e7a4d6-c57a-4e52-a6d6-becdd21929eb\" id=\"RenderManforKatanaReleaseNotes-KatanaLimitation\">Katana Limitation</h4><ul local-id=\"ef0dc6b7-da3c-4f33-af2e-734f25834ec6\"><li local-id=\"c6999044-99ad-43ef-965b-7c8a33a6b09b\"><p local-id=\"1acba637-30b6-4f4d-b046-2dd06c7e84d1\">If you use ROI and overscan or cropWindow, the ROI will have to be adjusted slightly after a resolution edit to get the correct value during a live render</p></li><li local-id=\"0522af8f-4aae-425d-a77c-84b3a19e25e6\"><p local-id=\"a9a1ce6b-55be-4064-b695-d9b15f9c58f5\">Instanced lights with filters using the &quot;Light Filter&quot; coordsys have an incorrect transform. The workaround is to promote the light filter to a shared light filter using a light filter reference.</p></li><li local-id=\"42335b07-4a79-4eb8-a230-50d026844223\"><p local-id=\"a774f84e-cb9e-41bc-8739-bef87c33ecaf\">We do not receive live render edits from Katana for nodes added at the end of the node graph, right above the Render node.&nbsp; If a no-op node (e.g. Merge) is inserted above the Render node and the node is added above that then the edit is received.</p></li><li local-id=\"373e6f34-6ead-4243-8b98-32b722115d67\"><p local-id=\"63af5d68-2327-4c7a-b014-2c6f3bd51337\">Any live updates will cause interactive motion blur to be disabled. The render must be restarted to see motion blur.</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"e53afdb3-be2e-4a68-b136-5f33818ab17e\" /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"300\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179753/inside-out-2-fear-01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531548866&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=300&amp;height=586\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179753/inside-out-2-fear-01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531548866&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1024\" data-width=\"524\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179767\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"inside-out-2-fear-01.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179753\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"10107872-8cbc-4053-af88-f9e3fef280d0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179753/inside-out-2-fear-01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531548866&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=524&amp;height=1024 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179753/inside-out-2-fear-01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531548866&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=300&amp;height=586 1x\" /></span><p local-id=\"a774be03-0c85-4c03-870a-4873062bde5f\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-colorid=\"b7brxvuad2\">Inside Out 2 &copy; Disney/Pixar</span></p>"
